<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-42-0682 </DOCNO><TEXT>The most important problem of underground storage of radioactive wastesin deep geologic formations is their long-term isolation from biosphere.For this reason ECN has done a project of the reservoir for high- andlow-level radioactive wastes in salt deposits. The 200 m layer of saltensures a safety of reservoir. 6 refs., 7 figs.</TEXT></DOC>